        <abstract> 
<p>Has sent CD’s letter to <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">8448</hi>].</p>  
<p>Expresses admiration for H. C. Bastian’s <hi rend="italic">The beginnings of life</hi> [1872] and comments on its bearing upon <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
